hopobject.body: What do you study? celebrex reddit New York Life has had good success with a deferred income annuity product introduced in 2011, called the guaranteed future income annuity (GFIA). It's sold over $1 billion in premiums since July 2011 introduction. The GFIA allows a buyer to set a future date to start receiving income, pay an initial premium as low as $5,000 and then continue to make additional premium contributions along the way. The product is aimed at buyers in their 50s.
